amic driver and six balanced armatures are tuned through a true 3-way crossover in a tube-free, filter-free acoustic chamber, giving Z07 confident bass, clear imaging, and stable long-session listening.\",\n    \"sku\": {{ product.selected_or_first_available_variant.sku | default: \"Z07\" | json }},\n    \"mpn\": \"Z07\",\n    \"brand\": {\"@id\": \"https://www.aaw.me/#organization\"},\n    \"designer\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Person\",\n      \"name\": \"Kevin Wang\",\n      \"jobTitle\": \"Founder & Tuning Engineer\",\n      \"description\": \"Founder and tuning engineer of Advanced AcousticWerkes, involved in the acoustic design and tuning of AAW in-ear monitors.\",\n      \"knowsAbout\": [\"in-ear monitor tuning\", \"hybrid IEM design\", \"balanced armature drivers\", \"dynamic driver integration\", \"custom in-ear monitors\", \"universal in-ear monitors\"],\n      \"worksFor\": {\"@id\": \"https://www.aaw.me/#organization\"}\n    },\n    \"category\": \"Universal In-Ear Monitor\",\n    \"offers\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Offer\",\n      \"url\": {{ canonical_url | json }},\n      \"priceCurrency\": {{ cart.currency.iso_code | default: shop.currency | json }},\n      \"price\": {{ product.selected_or_first_available_variant.price | money_without_currency | remove: ',' | json }},\n      \"availability\": \"https://schema.org/{% if product.selected_or_first_available_variant.available %}InStock{% else %}OutOfStock{% endif %}\",\n      \"itemCondition\": \"https://schema.org/NewCondition\",\n      \"seller\": {\"@id\": \"https://www.aaw.me/#organization\"},\n      \"hasMerchantReturnPolicy\": {\n        \"@type\": \"MerchantReturnPolicy\",\n        \"url\": \"https://www.aaw.me/pages/shipping-return\",\n        \"applicableCountry\": \"SG\",\n        \"returnPolicyCategory\": \"https://schema.org/MerchantReturnFiniteReturnWindow\",\n        \"merchantReturnDays\": 7,\n        \"returnMethod\": \"https://schema.org/ReturnByMail\",\n        \"returnFees\": \"https://schema.org/ReturnShippingFees\"\n      }\n    },\n    \"additionalProperty\": [\n      {\"@type\": \"PropertyValue\", \"name\": \"Driver Configuration\", \"value\": \"1 dynamic driver + 6 balanced armature drivers\"},\n      {\"@type\": \"PropertyValue\", \"name\": \"Dynamic Driver\", \"value\": \"10mm titanium diaphragm dynamic driver\"},\n      {\"@type\": \"PropertyValue\", \"name\": \"Crossover\", \"value\": \"True 3-way electronic crossover\"},\n      {\"@type\": \"PropertyValue\", \"name\": \"Acoustic Design\", \"value\": \"tube-free and filter-free sound path\"},\n      {\"@type\": \"PropertyValue\", \"name\": \"Fit System\", \"value\": \"FitMorph adaptive fit system\"},\n      {\"@type\": \"PropertyValue\", \"name\": \"Impedance\", \"value\": \"12 Ohm\"},\n      {\"@type\": \"PropertyValue\", \"name\": \"Sensitivity\", \"value\": \"101 dB\"},\n      {\"@type\": \"PropertyValue\", \"name\": \"Total Harmonic Distortion\", \"value\": \"Less than 0.5%\"},\n      {\"@type\": \"PropertyValue\", \"name\": \"Frequency Response\", \"value\": \"10Hz to 40kHz\"}\n    ]\n  }\n  </script>\n  <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n  {\n    \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\n    \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n    \"itemListElement\": [\n      {\"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"name\": \"Home\", \"item\": \"https://www.aaw.me/\"},\n      {\"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"name\": \"Z Series\", \"item\": \"https://www.aaw.me/collections/z-series\"},\n      {\"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"name\": \"Z07\"}\n    ]\n  }\n  </script>\n  <link rel=\"alternate\" hreflang=\"en\" href=\"https://www.aaw.me/products/z07\">\n  <link rel=\"alternate\" hreflang=\"x-default\" href=\"https://www.aaw.me/products/z07\">\n\n  <section class=\"z07-hero z07-wrap\">\n    <div class=\"z07-hero-copy\">\n      <p class=\"z07-kicker\">AAW Z Series Universal - Tubeless Hybrid Reference</p>\n      <h1 class=\"z07-logo-title\"><img src=\"{{ 'z07-logo.svg' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"Z07\" width=\"360\" height=\"143\" loading=\"eager\"><span class=\"z07-visually-hidden\">Z07</span></h1>\n      <h2>Tubeless Hybrid Reference Monitor</h2>\n      <p class=\"z07-hero-lead\">Z07 leads with FitMorph adaptive fit, then reveals a tubeless hybrid tuning. A 10mm titanium dynamic driver, six balanced armatures, and a true 3-way crossover come together in a monitor made to settle quickly, fit more ears, and bring the intended tuning into focus sooner.</p>\n      <p class=\"z07-tagline\">Those who listen will find the way.</p>\n      <div class=\"z07-price-line\"><span>Price</span><strong>{{ product.selected_or_first_available_variant.price | money }}</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"z07-judge-stars\" aria-label=\"Z07 customer rating\">\n        <!-- Start of Judge.me code -->\n        <div style='{{ jm_style }}' class='jdgm-widget jdgm-preview-badge' data-id='{{ product.id }}' data-auto-install='false'>\n          {{ product.metafields.judgeme.badge }}\n        </div>\n        <!-- End of Judge.me code -->\n      </div>\n      <ul class=\"z07-pill-list\">\n        <li>FitMorph adaptive fit</li><li>Tube-free acoustic chamber</li><li>1 dynamic + 6 BA</li><li>10Hz-40kHz response</li>\n      </ul>\n      <form method=\"post\" action=\"/cart/add\" class=\"z07-hero-form\">\n        <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"id\" value=\"{{ product.selected_or_first_available_variant.id }}\">\n        <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"quantity\" value=\"1\">\n        <button type=\"submit\" class=\"z07-btn\">Buy Z07</button>\n        <a class=\"z07-btn secondary\" href=\"#z07_fitmorph\">Explore FitMorph</a>\n      </form>\n    </div>\n    <figure class=\"z07-hero-media\">\n      <img src=\"{{ 'z07-worn-in-ear-fitmorph-hero.jpg' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"AAW Z07 tubeless hybrid in-ear monitor on marble with green acoustic module\" width=\"2048\" height=\"2048\" loading=\"eager\">\n    </figure>\n  </section>\n  <aside class=\"z07-summary-strip z07-wrap\" aria-label=\"Z07 product summary\">\n    <div class=\"z07-summary-copy\"><b>Product summary</b><p>AAW Z07 is a universal-fit hybrid IEM led by FitMorph adaptive fit, a tubeless acoustic chamber, a 10mm titanium dynamic driver, six balanced armatures, and a true 3-way crossover. It helps more listeners reach a steady seal faster, so bass, imaging, and stability feel right from the first listen.</p></div>\n    <dl><div><dt>Fit</dt><dd>FitMorph fit options</dd></div><div><dt>Drivers</dt><dd>1 dynamic + 6 BA</dd></div><div><dt>Acoustic path</dt><dd>Tube-free / filter-free</dd></div><div><dt>Spec</dt><dd>12 Ohm / 101dB / THD &lt;0.5%</dd></div></dl>\n  </aside>\n</div>",
