    "z07_architecture": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "section_visibility": "always",
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"z07-feature-shell\"><section id=\"z07_architecture\" class=\"z07-section dark z07-sound-section\"><div class=\"z07-wrap z07-grid-2\"><div><p class=\"z07-kicker\">Tubeless Sound Path</p><h2>A cleaner path from driver to ear</h2><div class=\"z07-callout\"><strong>Z07 sound path:</strong> each driver plays into a tube-free, filter-free acoustic chamber, helping Z07 sound cleaner and more immediate from bass to air.</div><p>Many multi-driver IEMs rely on tubes, dampers, and filters before the sound reaches your ear. Z07 takes a more direct route: once FitMorph gives you a secure seal, the tubeless chamber and true 3-way crossover help bass weight, vocal placement, and treble air arrive with less haze.</p><p>You hear the benefit as a quicker, cleaner presentation: titanium dynamic bass for weight, four balanced armatures for midrange body, and two balanced armatures for high-frequency air and space.</p><a class=\"z07-btn\" href=\"#z07_product_card\">View the driver layout</a></div><div class=\"z07-sound-card\"><img src=\"{{ 'z07-fitmorph-tubeless-sound-path-split-view-render.png' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"AAW Z07 split view showing FitMorph outer-ear support and tubeless sound path\" loading=\"lazy\"><div class=\"z07-mode-grid\"><article><span>Sub-bass / bass</span><h3>10mm Titanium Dynamic</h3><p>Deep extension, pressure control, and fast decay without midrange bloom.</p></article><article><span>Midrange / highs</span><h3>Six Balanced Armatures</h3><p>Quad BA mids and dual BA highs keep vocals, air, and imaging precisely layered.</p></article></div></div></div></section></div>",
