    "z07_product_card": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "section_visibility": "always",
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"z07-feature-shell\"><section id=\"z07_product_card\" class=\"z07-section dark z07-product-card-section\"><div class=\"z07-wrap\"><p class=\"z07-kicker\">At a glance</p><h2>What makes Z07 work</h2><article class=\"z07-spec-card\" aria-labelledby=\"z07-spec-card-title\"><header class=\"z07-spec-card-head\"><div class=\"z07-spec-lockup-text z07-spec-lockup-logo\"><span class=\"z07-spec-aaw\">AAW</span><span class=\"z07-spec-divider\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><img src=\"{{ 'z07-logo.svg' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"Z07\" width=\"206\" height=\"82\" loading=\"lazy\"></div><div class=\"z07-spec-edition\"><h3 id=\"z07-spec-card-title\">Tubeless Hybrid Reference Monitor</h3><p>10mm titanium dynamic driver, six balanced armatures, true 3-way crossover, FitMorph adaptive fit</p></div></header><div class=\"z07-driver-strip\" aria-label=\"Z07 driver and acoustic architecture\"><div class=\"z07-driver-item\"><span class=\"z07-icon z07-icon-woofer\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><b>1 x 10mm</b><small>Titanium Dynamic Driver</small></div><div class=\"z07-driver-item\"><span class=\"z07-icon z07-icon-quad-ba\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><b>4 x</b><small>Mid BA Drivers</small></div><div class=\"z07-driver-item\"><span class=\"z07-icon z07-icon-dual\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><b>2 x</b><small>High BA Drivers</small></div><div class=\"z07-driver-item\"><span class=\"z07-icon z07-icon-fitmorph\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><b>FitMorph</b><small>Adaptive Fit System</small></div></div><div class=\"z07-feature-panel\"><h3>Key Features</h3><ul><li>Tube-free and filter-free acoustic chamber</li><li>7-driver hybrid tuning</li><li>True 3-way electronic crossover</li><li>Precision aluminium body</li><li>Secure replaceable 0.78mm 2-pin connection</li><li>FitMorph adaptive fit system</li></ul><div class=\"z07-measurement-grid\" aria-label=\"Z07 electrical and acoustic measurements\"><article><span>Sensitivity</span><strong>101dB</strong></article><article><span>Impedance</span><strong>12 Ohm</strong></article><article><span>Total Harmonic Distortion</span><strong>&lt;0.5%</strong></article><article><span>Frequency Response</span><strong>10Hz-40kHz</strong></article><article><span>Crossover</span><strong>True 3-way</strong></article><article><span>Acoustic Design</span><strong>Tubeless / filter-free</strong></article></div></div><figure class=\"z07-fr-graph\"><img src=\"{{ 'z07-tubeless-hybrid-exploded-driver-layout.png' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"AAW Z07 exploded view showing FitMorph fit options, ear tip, precision aluminium body, balanced armatures, and tubeless faceplate assembly\" loading=\"lazy\"><figcaption><strong>Inside Z07.</strong> FitMorph fit options, the LiquidMorph tip, titanium dynamic driver, six balanced armatures, precision aluminium body, and tubeless faceplate assembly show how Z07 keeps fit and sound working together.</figcaption></figure></article></div></section></div>",
