        "section_visibility": "always",
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"z07-feature-shell\"><section class=\"z07-section dark z07-gallery-section\"><div class=\"z07-wrap\"><div class=\"z07-gallery-head\"><p class=\"z07-kicker\">Listening Notes</p><h2>What you notice when Z07 is in hand</h2><p class=\"z07-gallery-lead\">A closer look at the pieces that make Z07 different: the precision aluminium body, FitMorph fit system, secure 2-pin connection, LiquidMorph tips, and complete carry kit.</p></div><div class=\"z07-gallery-grid\"><figure tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" class=\"feature\"><img src=\"{{ 'z07-green-faceplate-closeup-black-tray.jpg' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"AAW Z07 green and black faceplate close-up\" loading=\"lazy\"><figcaption><b>Z07 faceplate</b><span>The green ring, open metal grille, and gold hardware give Z07 its instrument-like identity.</span></figcaption></figure><figure tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\"><img src=\"{{ 'z07-liquidmorph-ear-tips-teal-bore.jpg' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"LiquidMorph clear ear tips with teal inner bore for AAW Z07\" loading=\"lazy\"><figcaption><b>LiquidMorph tips</b><span>The canal seal stays silicone-based even when the outer-ear support is customized.</span></figcaption></figure><figure tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\"><img src=\"{{ 'z07-source-ready-cable-4-4mm-balanced-plug.jpg' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"AAW Z07 with cable and 4.4mm balanced plug\" loading=\"lazy\"><figcaption><b>Source-ready cable</b><span>A familiar 2-pin connection keeps Z07 flexible across portable and balanced sources.</span></figcaption></figure><figure tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\"><img src=\"{{ 'z07-complete-carry-case-monitor-kit.jpg' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"AAW Z07 carry case and included monitor kit\" loading=\"lazy\"><figcaption><b>Carry kit</b><span>The monitor, cable, and case are ready for repeated listening, packing, and travel.</span></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"z07-lightbox\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><button class=\"z07-lightbox-close\" type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Close image preview\">x</button><figure><img src=\"\" alt=\"\"><figcaption><b></b><span></span></figcaption></figure></div></div></section></div><script>(function(){function initZ07GalleryLightbox(){document.querySelectorAll('.z07-gallery-section').forEach(function(section){if(section.dataset.lightboxReady)return;section.dataset.lightboxReady='true';var lightbox=section.querySelector('.z07-lightbox');if(!lightbox)return;var lightImg=lightbox.querySelector('img');var lightTitle=lightbox.querySelector('figcaption b');var lightText=lightbox.querySelector('figcaption span');var close=lightbox.querySelector('.z07-lightbox-close');var lastTrigger=null;function openLightbox(figure){lastTrigger=figure;var img=figure.querySelector('img');var title=figure.querySelector('figcaption b');var text=figure.querySelector('figcaption span');lightImg.src=img.currentSrc||img.src;lightImg.alt=img.alt||'';lightTitle.textContent=title?title.textContent:'';lightText.textContent=text?text.textContent:'';lightbox.classList.add('is-open');lightbox.setAttribute('aria-hidden','false');document.documentElement.classList.add('z07-lightbox-open');close.focus();}function closeLightbox(){lightbox.classList.remove('is-open');lightbox.setAttribute('aria-hidden','true');document.documentElement.classList.remove('z07-lightbox-open');lightImg.removeAttribute('src');if(lastTrigger)lastTrigger.focus();}section.querySelectorAll('.z07-gallery-grid figure').forEach(function(figure){figure.addEventListener('click',function(){openLightbox(figure);});figure.addEventListener('keydown',function(event){if(event.key==='Enter'||event.key===' '){event.preventDefault();openLightbox(figure);}});});close.addEventListener('click',closeLightbox);lightbox.addEventListener('click',function(event){if(event.target===lightbox)closeLightbox();});document.addEventListener('keydown',function(event){if(event.key==='Escape'&&lightbox.classList.contains('is-open'))closeLightbox();});});}if(document.readyState==='loading')document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded',initZ07GalleryLightbox);else initZ07GalleryLightbox();})();</script>",
