      "settings": {
        "section_visibility": "always",
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"z07-feature-shell\"><section class=\"z07-section dark z07-fitment-section\"><div class=\"z07-wrap\"><div class=\"z07-section-head\"><p class=\"z07-kicker\">Consistent Fit, Consistent Sound</p><h2>Same Z07 tuning, whichever fit you choose</h2><p>Different shell shapes and canal angles can change what you hear. Z07 keeps the same tuning across its FitMorph options, so the sound you fall for is the sound you can keep enjoying.</p></div><div class=\"z07-fit-grid\"><figure><img src=\"{{ 'z07-model-wearing-universal-fit-over-ear-cable.jpg' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"Person wearing AAW Z07 universal in-ear monitor with over-ear cable\" loading=\"lazy\"><figcaption><b>Real-world fit check</b><span>The canal still seals with LiquidMorph tips, while FitMorph adjusts the outer support around your ear.</span></figcaption></figure><div class=\"z07-fit-points\"><article><span>01</span><h3>Audition with confidence</h3><p>The same Z07 tuning follows you whether you choose shark-fin, finless, or optional custom outer-ear support.</p></article><article><span>02</span><h3>Keep the silicone seal</h3><p>The ear tip still handles the canal seal, so custom outer-ear support changes how Z07 rests in the ear rather than changing the sound you chose.</p></article><article><span>03</span><h3>Less fit anxiety</h3><p>If one fit option feels wrong, Z07 gives you another fit route before you give up on the sound.</p></article></div></div></div></section></div>",
        "content_width": "large",
        "text_alignment": "left",
        "color_scheme": "primary",
        "top_space_desktop": 0,
        "bottom_space_desktop": 0,
        "top_space_mobile": 0,
