    "z07_engineering": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "section_visibility": "always",
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"z07-feature-shell\"><section class=\"z07-section dark z07-engineering-section\"><div class=\"z07-wrap z07-engineering-layout\"><div class=\"z07-engineering-copy-panel\"><p class=\"z07-kicker\">Craft & Sound</p><h2>A steadier sound for longer sessions</h2><p>Z07 uses a precision-machined aluminium body to keep its seven drivers working from the same stable base. The result is a monitor that keeps bass, vocals, and treble organized when the mix gets dense and the session gets long.</p><p>The 0.78mm 2-pin connection sits within the FitMorph fit system, giving Z07 a reassuring cable feel for everyday use. For the listener, that means fewer worries when swapping cables or carrying the monitor between sources.</p></div><figure class=\"z07-framed-image z07-engineering-visual\"><img src=\"{{ 'z07-industrial-design-sketch-line-art.jpg' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"AAW Z07 industrial design sketch of the FitMorph monitor body\" loading=\"lazy\"><figcaption>FitMorph helps Z07 feel settled first, so the music can take over without constant readjustment.</figcaption></figure><div class=\"z07-spec-table z07-engineering-spec-table\"><div><span>Format</span><b>Universal-fit tubeless hybrid IEM</b></div><div><span>Driver configuration</span><b>1 dynamic + 6 balanced armatures</b></div><div><span>Low end</span><b>10mm titanium diaphragm dynamic driver</b></div><div><span>Crossover</span><b>True 3-way electronic crossover</b></div><div><span>Body</span><b>Precision aluminium construction</b></div><div><span>Connection</span><b>Secure 0.78mm 2-pin design</b></div><div><span>Warranty</span><b>1-year warranty against manufacturing defects</b></div></div></div></section></div>",
        "content_width": "large",
        "text_alignment": "left",
        "color_scheme": "primary",
        "top_space_desktop": 0,
        "bottom_space_desktop": 0,
        "top_space_mobile": 0,
        "bottom_space_mobile": 0
      }
    },
    "z07_accessories": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "section_visibility": "always",
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"z07-feature-shell\"><section class=\"z07-section dark z07-accessories-section\"><div class=\"z07-wrap z07-accessories-layout\"><div class=\"z07-accessories-copy-panel\"><p class=\"z07-kicker\">Signal Chain Ready</p><h2>Ready for the sources you actually use</h2><p>Z07 ships ready for analog listening: swap between 3.5mm single-ended and 4.4mm balanced terminations for portable players, dongles, DAPs, and desktop DAC/amps. Its 12 Ohm impedance and 101dB sensitivity pair best with low-output-impedance sources for clean daily listening.</p><form method=\"post\" action=\"/cart/add\" class=\"z07-hero-form compact-form\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"id\" value=\"{{ product.selected_or_first_available_variant.id }}\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"quantity\" value=\"1\"><button type=\"submit\" class=\"z07-btn\">Buy Z07</button></form></div><figure class=\"z07-framed-image z07-accessories-media\"><img src=\"{{ 'z07-complete-carry-case-monitor-kit.jpg' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"AAW Z07 complete kit with carrying case, cable, 3.5mm and 4.4mm terminations, and monitors\" loading=\"lazy\"><figcaption>Z07 ships with a protective case, cable, and swappable 3.5mm / 4.4mm terminations for daily listening.</figcaption></figure><div class=\"z07-detail-list compact z07-accessories-options\"><div><b>Cable terminations</b><span>Interchangeable 3.5mm single-ended and 4.4mm balanced plugs are included.</span></div><div><b>Recommended source</b><span>Low-output-impedance portable player, dongle, DAP, or desktop DAC/amp.</span></div><div><b>IEM connection</b><span>0.78mm 2-pin connection through the FitMorph fit system.</span></div><div><b>Carry case</b><span>Protective case for daily transport and long-term storage.</span></div></div></div></section></div>",
