    "z07_where_to_buy": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "section_visibility": "always",
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"z07-feature-shell\"><section class=\"z07-section z07-where-section\"><div class=\"z07-wrap\"><div class=\"z07-where-head\"><div><p class=\"z07-kicker\">Where to buy</p><h2>Hear AAW in Singapore and beyond</h2></div><p>Advanced AcousticWerkes is based in Singapore. To audition Z07, arrange support, or find a dealer, start with AAW Singapore or one of the listening rooms below.</p></div><div class=\"z07-dealer-grid\"><article class=\"featured\"><span>Singapore locations</span><h3>AAW Office</h3><p>#01-03, 76 Playfair Rd, Singapore 367996<br>PH: +65 8731 5476<br>Email: sales@acousticwerkes.com<br>Hours: Monday, Wednesday, Thursday, Friday 10:00 AM-6:00 PM. Tuesday and Saturday by appointment. Sunday closed.</p></article><article><span>Singapore dealer</span><h3>Zeppelin & Co.</h3><p>1 Rochor Canal Rd, #02-78 Sim Lim Square, Singapore 188504<br>PH: 9337 9655<br>Hours: Daily 11:30 AM-8:00 PM; Sunday 12:00 PM-7:00 PM.</p></article><article><span>Singapore dealer</span><h3>JABEN</h3><p>1 Coleman St, #01-25 The Adelphi, Singapore 179803<br>PH: 6337 0809<br>Hours: Daily 12:00 PM-8:00 PM.</p></article><article><span>Singapore dealer</span><h3>AV One</h3><p>1 Coleman St, The Adelphi, Singapore 179803<br>PH: 6337 0080<br>Hours: Monday-Saturday 11:00 AM-7:30 PM; Sunday 1:00 PM-6:00 PM.</p></article></div><div class=\"z07-global-box\"><div><span>Global listening rooms</span><p>Outside Singapore, AAW works with specialist audio stores across Hong Kong, Macau, Japan, China, South Korea, and Thailand, including DMA, Fine Up Computer, Let's Go Audio, Music Movie Driver, e-earphone, Step Sound, Sorishop, and SoundProofBros.</p></div><a class=\"z07-btn secondary\" href=\"/pages/store-locator\">Find a listening room</a></div></div></section></div>",
